:'''Wen Furui:''' No problem. Ask me anything and we'll trade stories.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502012202_1005-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502012202_1005-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What are you doing in Xianzhou?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122103-->
::'''Wen Furui:''' Didn't I say I'm a transferred researcher to Xianzhou? Madam Herta does some work with Xianzhou, so all I need is approval from the locals.
::'''Wen Furui:''' I worked for the Department of Implement Arts. Have you heard of Xianzhou's Fallow Earth tech? If the negotiations go well, that'd be my research.
::'''Wen Furui:''' See, other than checking out the foxian ladies, I've got a purpose for being here.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Have you told any of the foxian ladies how you feel?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122107-->
::'''Wen Furui:''' Nope, nope, nope!
::'''Wen Furui:''' You know, despite giving courtship advice to countless colleagues of mine at the space station, I've never been in a relationship before. Plus, I'm rather shy...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I got it, say no more.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122110-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' Thanks, {{MC|f=sister|m=brother}}.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502122113-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122113-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' That's why I need your help. I'll see you when I'm ready.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} All talk, no action.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122112-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' You know everything, don't you?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502122113-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122113-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' That's why I need your help. I'll see you when I'm ready.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} I thought you were not interested in a relationship.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122115-->
::'''Wen Furui:''' ...That's in the past. The cosmos was the only thing on my mind back on the space station. Don't laugh, I'm serious.
::'''Wen Furui:''' When people asked me what's my type, I'd say, "No one's my type."
::'''Wen Furui:''' Until I met a foxian lady. It turned out I wasn't looking for anybody because I had never met anyone like her.
::'''Wen Furui:''' I couldn't wait to get here after realizing that. I'm eager to start a new life.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Let's talk again sometime.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122120-->
::'''Wen Furui:''' No problem, {{MC|f=sister|m=brother}}. I scratch your back and you scratch mine.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Wen Furui:''' No problem, {{MC|f=sister|m=brother}}. I scratch your back and you scratch mine.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Wen Furui:''' I pay to commute by air every day just so I can see the lovely foxian pilots. All that cost aside, they've stopped taking passengers lately...
:'''Wen Furui:''' I can't be banned, can I? But how do you explain that they only let me pick from the male pilots when I try to book a flight?
:'''Wen Furui:''' There you are. Have something to talk to me about?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000089: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502012201.json-->
::'''Wen Furui:''' It's me, (Trailblazer). Do you still remember me? I'm Wen Furui. I asked you to deliver something back when we were at the Herta Space Station.
::'''Wen Furui:''' I always wanted Asta, the acting lead researcher, to transfer me, and now here I am in the foxian capital I've dreamed about. Thanks to you!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I feel sorry for the foxians in Xianzhou now.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122015-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' Hey, don't make me out to be some sort of monster! I've got a good rep. Just ask the folks over at the space station.
:::'''Wen Furui:''' Not to mention I came to Xianzhou with the purpose of engaging in trade and academic exchange.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Foxian... capital?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122018-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' Isn't Xianzhou the capital of the foxians?
:::'''Wen Furui:''' You don't seem to agree... Am I the only one who thinks that?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Asta made an egregious call.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122021-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' Pfft, don't say that. I worked hard to get myself transferred out of there.
:::'''Wen Furui:''' ...Not to mention it's an internal space station matter and none of your business.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502122023-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122023-->
::'''Wen Furui:''' I've been in Xianzhou for a while now and see many foxian ladies every day. But do you know which one I care about the most?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502012201_977-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502012201_977-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Madam Yukong?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122025-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' She is very charming, but I see her as a star to appreciate from afar. She's beyond my approach.
:::'''Wen Furui:''' Can't you see she's out of my league?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Nope.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122028-->
::::'''Wen Furui:''' I treated you like a confidant, but I see you're not quite ready yet.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Maybe...?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122030-->
::::'''Wen Furui:''' Watch and learn and you'll be like me in no time.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You're weird.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122032-->
::::'''Wen Furui:''' Don't judge me by worldly norms.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm not interested in that.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122034-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' I see, you're not one for conversations, are you?
:::'''Wen Furui:''' At least pretend like you're interested...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You should be more low-key.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122037-->
:::'''Wen Furui:''' I get it. Unlike the true scoundrels, I have principles. So relax.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502122038-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502122038-->
